name: SafeCookie
description: This project is created to prove ourselves and you that a community guided project can reach great achievements. Our plan is simple: make you believe that by being part of Safecookie gives you the power to make wealth while having a word to say in the project’s future. The team has vast experience in taking part on many Crypto related projects and we consider Safecookie as our baby: this being the reason of renouncing the ownership and therefore proving the desire of wanting to stay with you and growing together. This project will allow you to mint your own NFT and also sell them on our marketplace and therefore you’re chances to getting the financial freedom you want is at your fingertips. Be part of something huge and enjoy the ride!
